Articles.Content:
I haven't used Impact in awhile, nice to see the mod working in KSP 1.2.2. I also made a <abbr title="Module Manager (mod)">MM</abbr> patch to add the impact sensor to the stock accelerometer:

@PART[sensorAccelerometer]:NEEDS[kerbal-impact]  

{  

MODULE

    {

        name = Seismometer

    }  

}
